    "title": "Immediate Requirement Logistics Manager at Evergreen India",
    "description": "Join the Evergreen India family as a Logistics Manager in Vijayawada. We believe in empowering our employees with the tools, training, and environment they need to succeed.\n\nAbout Evergreen India:\nEvergreen India is a leading organization in the On-site sector, committed to excellence, innovation, and employee growth. We offer a dynamic work environment where talent is recognized and rewarded.\n\nKey Responsibilities:\n• Conduct periodic vendor audits and evaluate logistics partners\n• Implement warehouse management systems (WMS) and track KPIs\n• Manage relationships with third-party logistics providers\n• Oversee end-to-end logistics operations for timely delivery\n• Manage reverse logistics and return merchandise authorization\n• Track shipments in real-time and resolve delivery exceptions\n• Coordinate with warehousing teams for inbound and outbound operations\n\nRequired Skills & Qualifications:\n• Diploma or Degree in Hospitality Management\n• 0-1 years of relevant experience\n• Proficiency in ERP Systems\n• Proficiency in WMS\n• Proficiency in SAP SCM\n• Proficiency in Route Optimization\n• Proficiency in Fleet Management\n• Proficiency in Data Analytics\n• Proficiency in MS Excel\n• Proficiency in TMS\n\nWork Mode: On-site - Work from our office\n\nWhat We Offer:\n• Recognition and rewards programs\n• Flexible working hours\n• Work-from-home flexibility\n• Maternity and paternity leave\n• Referral bonus program\n• Mobile and internet reimbursement\n• Salary Range: 2.5 LPA - 6 LPA per annum\n\nLocation: Vijayawada, Andhra Pradesh, India\n\nIf you are excited about this opportunity, apply now and take the next step in your career journey with Evergreen India!",
